==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: bum
<hw>bum</hw> <pr>(b⟦ucr⟧m)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To borrow without
intention of returning; to cadge; <as>as, to <ex>bum</ex> a cigarette;
to <ex>bum</ex> a cup of coffee</as>; -- usually with inexpensive items
as the object.</def> <mark>[informal]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bum</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 4 ====
