<hw>Bum</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A humming noise.</def>
<rj><au>Halliwell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bumbailiff</ent>⟦br⟧
